Irish combine
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a home-made flail seed-thrasher consisting two stout sticks coupled together by a bullock hide thong [1800s - early 1900s.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
